title: Building a Cake Empire From Scratch
itunes:title: Building a Cake Empire From Scratch
description:
Susan Sarich, Founder and CEO of SusieCakes, discusses turning her grandmother’s recipes into a thriving bakery business.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
